					<div class="bio">
						<h4>Philippe Sands</h4>
												<p>Philippe Sands is an international lawyer and a professor of law at University College London. He is the author of <em>Lawless World</em> and <em>Torture Team</em> and is a frequent commentator on CNN and the BBC World Service. Sands lectures around the world and has taught at New York University and been a visiting professor at the University of Toronto, the University of Melbourne, and the Université de Paris I (Sorbonne). In 2003 he was appointed a Queen’s Counsel. He lives in London, England.</p>
